#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.loggamma.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.loggamma"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.loggamma:1 of
msgid "Principal branch of the logarithm of the gamma function."
msgstr "伽马函数对数的主分支。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.loggamma:3 of
msgid ""
"Defined to be :math:`\\log(\\Gamma(x))` for :math:`x > 0` and extended to"
" the complex plane by analytic continuation. The function has a single "
"branch cut on the negative real axis."
msgstr ""
"定义为 :math:`x > 0` 时的 :math:`\\log(\\Gamma(x))`，并通过解析延拓扩展到"
"复平面。该函数在负实轴上有一个分支切割。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.loggamma.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.loggamma:8 of
msgid "Values in the complex plane at which to compute ``loggamma``"
msgstr "要在其中计算 ``loggamma`` 的复平面上的值"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.loggamma:10 of
msgid "Output array for computed values of ``loggamma``"
msgstr "用于存储 ``loggamma`` 计算结果的输出数组"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.loggamma.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.loggamma:13 of
msgid "**loggamma** -- Values of ``loggamma`` at z."
msgstr "**loggamma** -- 在 z 处的 ``loggamma`` 值。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.loggamma.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.loggamma:18 of
msgid ":py:obj:`gammaln`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.loggamma:19 of
msgid "logarithm of the absolute value of the gamma function"
msgstr "伽马函数绝对值的对数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.loggamma:21 of
msgid ":py:obj:`gammasgn`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.loggamma:22 of
msgid "sign of the gamma function"
msgstr "伽马函数的符号"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.loggamma:25 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.loggamma:26 of
msgid ""
"It is not generally true that :math:`\\log\\Gamma(z) = "
"\\log(\\Gamma(z))`, though the real parts of the functions do agree. The "
"benefit of not defining `loggamma` as :math:`\\log(\\Gamma(z))` is that "
"the latter function has a complicated branch cut structure whereas "
"`loggamma` is analytic except for on the negative real axis."
msgstr ""
"通常来说，:math:`\\log\\Gamma(z) = \\log(\\Gamma(z))` 并不成立，尽管这"
"两个函数的实部是一致的。不将 `loggamma` 定义为 :math:`\\log(\\Gamma(z))` "
"的好处在于后者的分支切割结构较为复杂，而 `loggamma` 除了在负实轴上之外是"
"解析的。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.loggamma:33 of
msgid "The identities"
msgstr "恒等式"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.loggamma:35 of
msgid ""
"\\exp(\\log\\Gamma(z)) &= \\Gamma(z) \\\\\n"
"\\log\\Gamma(z + 1) &= \\log(z) + \\log\\Gamma(z)\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.loggamma:39 of
msgid "make `loggamma` useful for working in complex logspace."
msgstr "使得 `loggamma` 在复数对数空间中非常有用。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.loggamma:41 of
msgid ""
"On the real line `loggamma` is related to `gammaln` via ``exp(loggamma(x "
"+ 0j)) = gammasgn(x)*exp(gammaln(x))``, up to rounding error."
msgstr ""
"在实数轴上，`loggamma` 与 `gammaln` 之间的关系是 ``exp(loggamma(x + 0j)) "
"= gammasgn(x)*exp(gammaln(x))``，忽略舍入误差。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.loggamma:45 of
msgid "The implementation here is based on [hare1997]_."
msgstr "这里的实现基于 [hare1997]_。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.loggamma:48 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.loggamma:49 of
msgid ""
"D.E.G. Hare, *Computing the Principal Branch of log-Gamma*, Journal of "
"Algorithms, Volume 25, Issue 2, November 1997, pages 221-236."
msgstr ""

